snippet.title: The UnMaking - Doom 64 MegaWAD Trailer
snippet.description:
The UnMaking is a mapset for Doom 64 released in December 2020. It was originally designed for Doom 64 EX, but a new and expanded version for the official Steam rerelease is out as of November 2021.

You can get The UnMaking on Doomworld: https://www.doomworld.com/forum/topic/125606/

(This trailer is basically just me remaking the Babylon 5 season 5 title sequence with worse editing skills, so that's where the music is from if you were wondering. Whoever owns Babylon 5 nowadays please don't come for me.)
